===========================================================
ABillS - ~AsmodeuS~ Billing System.
Version: 0.50
-----------------------------------------------------------
Open Source Billing Solution
===========================================================



Billing system with different abilities:
   Prepaid & Postpaid Services
   Prepaid Cards 
   Dialup/VPN (PPPoE, PPTP, L2TP, IPSec) 
   Hotspot
   NetFlow 
   Squid Monitoring 
   VoIP (GNU gatekeeper, Asterisk) 
   CMTS (BSR1000 monitoring) 
   Mail management (Postfix, Spamassassin, Courier IMAP/POP) 
   SNMP Monitoring (D-Link, Cisco, Zyxel, Patton, Mikrotik) 
   Cisco ISG (Services, Turbo Mode) 
   IPTV (VoD,nVoD)
   Antivirus (Dr. Web, AV Desk)

Technology: 
   FreeBSD, Linux, MySQL, Radius, DHCP, Netwlow, SNMP, SMTP


Site: 
   http://abills.net.ua
